column2: SELECT TOP #     COUNT(Track.AlbumId) AS Num_tracks,     SUM(Track.UnitPrice) As Price FROM chinook.Album album INNER JOIN chinook.Track track ON album.AlbumId = track.AlbumId INNER JOIN chinook.Artist artist ON album.ArtistId = artist.ArtistId GROUP BY album.AlbumId ORDER BY SUM(Track.UnitPrice) DESC
